cards.name: Arcane Enigma
cards.description: Unleash the mysteries of the arcane with this legendary card. It holds the power to manipulate luck and weave protective spells.

cards.name: Spectral Mirage
cards.description: Summon ethereal illusions with this mythical card. It confounds enemies and boosts the agility of its wielder.

cards.name: Celestial Harmony
cards.description: Attain balance with the celestial forces using this divine card. It enhances both offensive and defensive capabilities.

cards.name: Eclipse Veil
cards.description: Shroud yourself in the mystique of the eclipse with this enigmatic card. It grants unparalleled protection and dark powers.

cards.name: Astral Guardian
cards.description: Summon a celestial guardian with this divine card. It shields its wielder from harm and retaliates with divine retribution.

cards.name: Lunar Eclipse Blade
cards.description: Channel the power of a lunar eclipse with this formidable card. It cuts through enemies with precision and darkness.

cards.name: Soulbound Specter
cards.description: Bind your enemies' souls with this spectral card. It drains life force and haunts foes with ghostly apparitions.
